  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505139111\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb08IU7YZ6ic1yHEUVwWMUWHgb0Szhs3tzqoeMmUdtNo4SEb40uwJAxMZ4gu3DKw5Uo1F6eTMSibicd3A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e0a6327&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb08IU7YZ6ic1yHEUVwWMUWHgb0Szhs3tzqoeMmUdtNo4SEb40uwJAxMZ4gu3DKw5Uo1F6eTMSibicd3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">AI写论文早就不稀奇了，可如今，它甚至能提出实验方案，设计出能被验证的分子。今年10月，AI将更进一步，走上学术舞台。在一场名为Agents4Science的会议上，它不仅要当第一作者、评审，还要亲自上台报告。这不只是一次会议，更像是一场公开的实验。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-top: 24px;text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">去年，斯坦福学者James Zou搭建了一个「虚拟实验室」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">五个AI科学家，分工协作，最终提出了纳米抗体方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验验证有效，还登上了《Nature》。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，他又有了一个更激进的尝试——Agents4Science大会。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一次，AI不再只是幕后助手，而是要当第一作者、审稿人，甚至报告人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI登上学术舞台</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一场前所未有的会议</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今年10月，这场名为Agents4Science的线上学术会议即将开幕。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138944\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4246885617214043\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1766\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1766\" data-height=\"750\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"245\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8f7aa437&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsN71cCJhvE3Ll4m7szxia0UCBXhBMyYcXgsNYcbZG8AnRTnfIkcsrlzLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不是噱头，而是一次被精心设计的科研试验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">主办方明确规定，所有论文都必须由AI担任第一作者，人类研究者只能作为顾问，并且要在文稿里披露双方的分工。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">提交的研究也有限制：只接受AI主导的计算型成果，那些严重依赖湿实验的数据不会被接收。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">评审环节同样大胆：初审由多个不同模型的AI互相打分，最后才交由人类专家委员会终审。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505139190\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.41730103806228375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1445\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"241\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c8ae5190&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb08IU7YZ6ic1yHEUVwWMUWHguicVCzhI9coN8kIT1LJHJHEt8pKyRkwAvKlsQwQI6dnYXIhibw2AVemg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所有评审意见以及所用模型的信息都会对外公开。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">主办方甚至计划在会后发布一份元分析，系统评估AI在写作和审稿中到底能走多远。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除了这些规则，会议还设定了三个核心目标：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">探测边界（Inquiry）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：在公开透明的环境里，检验AI在科研发现中的真正潜力与局限。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">建立规范（Establishing norms）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：为署名、验证和伦理问题制定标准，让学术界提前做好准备。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">提升透明度（Transparency）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：要求全面披露AI的参与情况，并将提示词和评审意见作为开放资源，让外界清晰看到AI的角色。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505139188\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5781466113416321\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1446\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"334\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=312b3159&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb08IU7YZ6ic1yHEUVwWMUWHgx3KWKI2qYiaE8PLw0ibeELic79Px8cyvZHyLcKZTyhiaQGfSYSP4ia6FpicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从署名到评审，再到最后的展示，AI被推上了学术舞台的每一个关键环节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一切背后，都指向同一个人——James Zou。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"metfcuxdjjf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138943\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4423076923076923\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"364\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"364\" data-height=\"525\" data-backw=\"364\" data-backh=\"525\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=29076434&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsNp3UhOc5C9fHWp6x9b9iaSUDicN7wzBeqvU7g1x0osgy8nCAibzSZXVnibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他是斯坦福大学的计算机科学家，长期研究人机协作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">去年，他曾搭建过一个「虚拟实验室」，最终在顶级期刊上发表成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作为会议主席之一，Zou表示会议将公开所有提交的论文和评论，以便研究人员和审稿人能够透明地研究AI的优势和局限性。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「我们预计AI会犯错误，公开研究这些错误将非常有启发性！」</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138946\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3660968660968662\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"702\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"702\" data-height=\"959\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"768\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5be55503&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsNxXhZmgOdt8vHvammFx8rtVic1w44huHklDaneYmx0J8oBLNcSK7lQ1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不少网友也纷纷表示期待和愿意为这次史无前例的学术会议投稿。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138947\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3299620733249051\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"791\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"791\" data-height=\"1052\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"747\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32104a9d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsNyrcPJ2d3KTBxZSP9jCaibQ3vYdOwPsUZRhaJHQribC27NicRDVOgR0y6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">从推理到验证</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">虚拟实验室的惊人结果</span></strong></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这场会议之前，James Zou已经进行过一次引人注目的尝试。</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他搭建了一个「虚拟实验室」，这个实验室由五个专精不同方向的AI智能体组成：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有人负责免疫学，有人专攻计算生物学，还有人扮演实验室的负责人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些AI科学家被赋予同一个研究目标——寻找新冠治疗方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"metfd9jv27a\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138949\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9501845018450185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"542\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"542\" data-height=\"515\" data-backw=\"542\" data-backh=\"515\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37c11a80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsNXHhReE7xPLPkIsUYHTYLEAFccvWwL7PmiazXKwZNIQNJx2iaPmLSfwHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">经过多轮讨论与推演，它们最终将注意力集中在「纳米抗体」这一方向上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">理由听起来出乎意料：由于计算资源有限，体积更小的纳米抗体比常规分子更适合在模拟中高效生成和筛选。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果证明，这一推理并非空想。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Zou的团队随后对AI设计出的候选分子进行了验证，发现它们确实能够结合新冠病毒的关键靶点，相关成果最终发表于《Nature》。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138945\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.31527093596059114\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1015\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1015\" data-height=\"320\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"177\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4a5d1fd1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsNia8P5VnQyQ9DY6ZE7qTJnqp23yKQVYXUbJl0rDORWlkgFf1AnokN8Qw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Zou看来，这并不是AI替代科学家的标志，而是一个重要信号：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI能够像科研团队一样分工协作，提出方案并自洽地解释理由。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505139189\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6135265700483091\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1035\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"355\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c3460c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb08IU7YZ6ic1yHEUVwWMUWHgElqGfaBEiarDxIxveSzWq0vt1AeRib61yKPNVmMqJjqZPmpbZZiaJLia6Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"metfe8vgplk\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"metfe8vp1zdp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">虚拟实验室团队会议摘录，具有独特角色的AI智能体在会议上讨论抗体项目</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但事实上，AI能在虚拟环境里预测蛋白质结构、模拟分子结合、筛选材料晶格，却无法真正走入实验室，更不会知道反应结果是否危险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">至于灵光一现的「洞察力」，AI更是缺乏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也就是说，AI更像是一个实验员，把几千条路线尝试一遍后，再把最有把握的交给人类。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">怀疑的声音</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">洞察力与责任归属之争</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI实验的故事听上去精彩，但不是所有科学家都买账。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">耶鲁大学的Lisa Messeri就提出质疑：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI或许能在数据中找出规律，却缺乏真正的「洞察力跳跃」。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果科研只是机械的推理，那么创新性的突破从何而来？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">普林斯顿大学的认知科学家Molly Crockett则担心另一件事：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">过度依赖AI，是否会让年轻科研人员失去最宝贵的训练机会？</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验失败、思路受挫、反复试错，这些本是科研成长的必经之路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果AI替代了这部分过程，科研经历算不算被「注水」？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他主张让更多学科专家参与到实践之中，深思熟虑后设计出实验，最后再让AI审查。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138953\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5829596412556054\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"892\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"892\" data-height=\"520\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"328\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15647c2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsNPPiaiaTrXnUlvicQZ0WZiagguDYI3mTXWNTm8NJmg7basm90iaxCx4jNPSg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更现实的问题是，当前的学术规范严格禁止AI被列为作者——COPE、ICMJE、ACS 等权威指南都强调：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI无权承担准确性与伦理责任，所有科研最终仍由人类负责。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这样看来，场大会不仅是一次技术试验，更是在挑战学术界的制度红线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">下一步</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">主导者是人类还是AI？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对James Zou来说，这场会议更像一次公开实验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他直言：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「也许AI会带来惊人的发现，也可能只是一些有趣的错误。」</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论结果如何，他想要的是真实数据——</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让学术界看到AI到底能做到哪里，而不是只靠想象与炒作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，美国政府已经在AI行动计划中提出，要投资「自动化云实验室」。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138951\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6044176706827309\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"996\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"996\" data-height=\"602\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"340\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c59a54e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0mRiaAib8vW8Bjch1lj1RKsNctKs4iba15COFVeGMIbiaDF7tIKDIBiaPsC6hWibQmxEeAaJ5SR9MJdpsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，在制度和资金支持下，「AI科学家」或许会越来越多地介入科研流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果未来科研方向越来越多地由AI主导，人类会是它的合作伙伴，还是实验室里的助手？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">或许这才是Agents4Science真正抛给我们的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.technologyreview.com/2025/08/22/1122304/ai-scientist-research-autonomous-agents/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.technologyreview.com/2025/08/22/1122304/ai-scientist-research-autonomous-agents/</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://agents4science.stanford.edu/faq.html?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://agents4science.stanford.edu/faq.html?utm_source=chatgpt.com</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://agents4science.stanford.edu/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://agents4science.stanford.edu/?utm_source=chatgpt.com</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "斯坦福大学首创“AI 科学家大会”，首次让 AI 担任论文一作、评审和报告人，探索 AI 在科研中的潜力与伦理挑战。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "斯坦福大学首创“AI 科学家大会”，首次让 AI 担任论文一作、评审和报告人，探索 AI 在科研中的潜力与伦理挑战。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了斯坦福大学 James Zou 教授发起的一场名为“Agents4Science”的线上学术会议。该会议旨在推动 AI 在科学研究中的角色，首次明确规定所有提交论文必须由 AI 担任第一作者，人类研究者作为顾问，并需披露 AI 参与细节。评审环节也由 AI 模型进行初审，再交由人类专家终审，所有评审意见和模型信息将公开。会议设定了探测 AI 科研边界、建立学术规范和提升透明度三大核心目标。文章还回顾了 James Zou 此前构建的“虚拟实验室”，其中 AI 科学家团队成功设计出纳米抗体并发表于《Nature》。尽管 AI 在推理和验证方面展现出强大能力，但文章也提出了质疑，如 AI 缺乏“洞察力跳跃”、可能影响年轻科研人员的培养，以及当前学术界对 AI 作者身份的伦理和责任归属争议。最终，会议被视为一项公开实验，旨在通过真实数据揭示 AI 在科研中的实际能力和局限性，并引发对未来科研中人与 AI 主导地位的深刻思考。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "“Agents4Science”会议开创 AI 担任学术主角的先河",
      "explanation": "会议首次明确 AI 为论文第一作者、评审和报告人，旨在通过公开实验探索 AI 在科研发现中的真实潜力与局限，挑战传统学术规范。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 智能体已具备协作式科研与验证能力",
      "explanation": "James Zou 教授的“虚拟实验室”案例表明，AI 智能体能分工协作，提出可验证的科学方案，并成功设计出纳米抗体，证明其在计算型研究中的效用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 在科研中的角色引发伦理与洞察力争议",
      "explanation": "有学者质疑 AI 缺乏真正的“洞察力”，可能影响年轻科研人员的成长，且当前学术规范禁止 AI 作为作者，凸显了责任归属和伦理挑战。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 写论文早就不稀奇了，可如今，它甚至能提出实验方案，设计出能被验证的分子。",
    "主办方明确规定，所有论文都必须由 AI 担任第一作者，人类研究者只能作为顾问，并且要在文稿里披露双方的分工。",
    "我们预计 AI 会犯错误，公开研究这些错误将非常有启发性！",
    "AI 或许能在数据中找出规律，却缺乏真正的「洞察力跳跃」。",
    "如果未来科研方向越来越多地由 AI 主导，人类会是它的合作伙伴，还是实验室里的助手？"
